WEBVTT

00:00:00.456 --> 00:00:04.288
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord! It's Brandon and Diana again.

00:00:04.289 --> 00:00:08.895
We have some things on our heart today, folks. We're in the last of the last days here.

00:00:08.896 --> 00:00:19.159
Jesus is coming, things are getting serious, and people say, 'Brandon, that kind of scares me.'You should be scared if you don't know Jesus.

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:24.329
You should be flat terrified if you don't have Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal savior.

00:00:24.330 --> 00:00:33.362
It should just plum freak you out if you don't have Jesus as your Lord and personal savior because you are in trouble.

00:00:33.363 --> 00:00:53.367
This is the time right now, as we speak, to yield yourself and say, 'Jesus, I need a savior.'You have the opportunity today to make Jesus Christ your Lord and personal savior; to say today, 'I choose to follow Jesus.'No one is promised tomorrow.

00:00:53.368 --> 00:00:58.529
Have you driven by a massive graveyard and seen all those people?

00:00:58.530 --> 00:01:05.584
I always wonder how many of those people went to hell and how many went to heaven.

00:01:05.585 --> 00:01:13.788
Everybody has a choice, but everybody thinks they have a long time to make a choice, and some of you only have today.

00:01:13.789 --> 00:01:20.276
Some of you will not make it out of your sleep tonight; some of you won't make it out of your week.

00:01:20.277 --> 00:01:24.330
You are not promised tomorrow; you're only promised right now.

00:01:24.331 --> 00:01:30.273
I believe with all my heart that God is going to give us long life, and He said He'd satisfy us and show us His salvation.

00:01:30.274 --> 00:01:35.015
I believe for 120 years. You believe for all this stuff, but sometimes things happen.

00:01:35.016 --> 00:01:45.329
I'm just trying to make you think about eternity today. Think about eternity.

00:01:45.330 --> 00:02:13.270
If you look at all the stars in space, if you look at all the grains of sand on the beach, and every single one of those little pieces of grain of sand represent a year—you can count all the sand on a beach, you can count all the stars in the galaxies and the universe, and you still will be counting and counting.

00:02:13.272 --> 00:02:16.412
Eternity is forever, and so that's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:02:16.413 --> 00:02:20.739
If you really look at how big eternity is, your mind can't comprehend it.

00:02:20.740 --> 00:02:26.049
You can never count all the sand on a beach or the stars in the sky.

00:02:26.050 --> 00:02:41.311
Even if you did, eternity is far greater than that. So I want you to focus on your eternity.

00:02:41.312 --> 00:02:47.112
Where will you spend eternity? You don't turn into some kind of nothingness.

00:02:47.113 --> 00:02:53.896
We don't have reincarnation and come back as a butterfly or a dog or a cat.

00:02:53.897 --> 00:02:59.398
No, the Bible says it's appointed unto man once to die, and after that the judgment.

00:02:59.399 --> 00:03:04.639
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord or to be present in hell, folks.

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:10.193
Where will you go and spend eternity? That's what you have to ask yourself as you watch this today.

00:03:10.194 --> 00:03:19.763
Yes, all this stuff is going on, and I'm telling you tragic things I've seen—very sobering, dark days ahead.

00:03:19.764 --> 00:03:30.359
Most people say, 'Well, that's not for me.'A lot of people in the Christian community do not want to hear it because they think we're going to pray it all away.

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:36.990
Folks, things happen, and I want to tell you COVID wasn't prayed away like you all thought it would be.

00:03:36.991 --> 00:03:48.359
I saw a storm coming and the Lord told me this was a storm to wake up everybody. Did He create the storm? Did He create COVID? No.

00:03:48.360 --> 00:04:05.192
But the Lord told me, 'I've yelled and yelled to tell my bride to wake up, to tell my body to wake up.'He said, 'Brandon, what happens to a child if you keep telling them to get up?

00:04:05.193 --> 00:04:16.198
What's the next thing you do?'He said, 'You shake them.'A great shaking to awaken is about to take place.

00:04:16.199 --> 00:04:25.590
And He told me this: 'If the church does not wake up after this shaking, there will be another shaking.

00:04:25.591 --> 00:04:47.870
A greater wave, a greater shaking is coming for the church.'We saw a lot of people wake up during this timeframe, but there are still billions that are asleep, that do not see how close we are to the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:04:47.871 --> 00:04:57.298
They rouse themselves and then just fall back asleep. They look up and go, 'Oh, okay,'and they go back to sleep. That's what happened.

00:04:57.299 --> 00:05:05.057
So now I really believe, whenever Jonathan Cahn talked about the lightning strikes, I thought that was amazing.

00:05:05.058 --> 00:05:16.211
I encourage you to go watch that video, Jonathan Cahn's lightning strike.

00:05:16.212 --> 00:05:28.983
He talked about how lightning struck the One World Trade Center, the Empire State Building, the Capitol, and the Washington Monument, and he said this was not coincidence.

00:05:28.984 --> 00:05:39.570
It all happened before the new year of 2025. It's a sign. I thought it was interesting it was four again.

00:05:39.571 --> 00:05:48.180
The Lord told me, 'I'm giving you a four-year window for a massive harvest.

00:05:48.181 --> 00:06:13.493
I'm giving you a reprieve from what was coming, a major reprieve from a great acceleration of the Antichrist agenda upon this earth.'I told you we were at the end of the last Shemitah cycle timeframe of this last Rosh Hashanah.

00:06:13.494 --> 00:06:27.626
And He told me, 'Adam's lease is up.'But He's giving us a sliver of time to bring in the harvest.

00:06:27.627 --> 00:06:40.052
Satan is petitioning for the seven-year Tribulation, saying time is up.

00:06:40.053 --> 00:06:44.322
That's where we are, folks, and God's giving us this little window.

00:06:44.323 --> 00:06:54.832
I believe through Trump's presidency of these four years, the four lightning strikes, the four oak trees I've told you about—the Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm kicking this down the road.

00:06:54.833 --> 00:07:05.433
I'm giving you a window. I want a harvest.'Jesus held out His hands with those massive holes and said, 'I am the Lord of the harvest.

00:07:05.434 --> 00:07:30.458
Will you help me? For I died for every single one of them.'He wants every single one of you to have the opportunity to choose heaven today.

00:07:30.459 --> 00:07:40.025
You're here because you want to know about terrorist attacks; I'm telling you something much worse is coming than you could ever imagine: it's called hell.

00:07:40.026 --> 00:08:09.132
You have the opportunity today to choose heaven. God didn't create hell for human beings; He created it for the devil and his demons.

00:08:09.133 --> 00:08:23.313
He created heaven for you, but it's a choice. Whom will you serve this day?

00:08:23.314 --> 00:08:37.636
As for me and my house, we're serving the Lord. Jesus Christ is the only way to heaven.

00:08:37.637 --> 00:08:55.232
Not Buddha, not Muhammad, not any kind of false god. I got an email from a guy saying there's a lot of ways to heaven.

00:08:55.233 --> 00:09:36.626
No, sir, you are deceived by a demonic spirit. The only way is the Lord Jesus Christ. We believe on this channel that He's coming soon.

00:09:36.627 --> 00:10:16.327
I had a guy email saying he wants to party in his 20s and give his heart to Jesus in ten years.

00:10:16.328 --> 00:10:41.520
Is that a serious question? God's not good enough for you right now?

00:10:41.521 --> 00:10:55.869
That's the attitude of a lot of people, and I say, 'Woe to you,'because there will be a day you stand before the Father and give an account for everything you've done.

00:10:55.870 --> 00:11:24.039
He will either know you or say, 'Depart from me, I never knew you.'It's a bad eternity for you.

00:11:24.040 --> 00:11:31.333
I've seen a great economic crisis beyond comprehension. The Lord said it was delayed for a window.

00:11:31.334 --> 00:11:46.342
There's a word for my body, for the people who are on fire and filled with the Holy Spirit, to have their lamps full of oil.

00:11:46.343 --> 00:12:00.679
And for the ones living lukewarm, there's a separate word: there will be a great shaking to awaken again for them.

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:23.763
He's a God of mercy, giving one last chance to get on the boat.

00:12:23.764 --> 00:12:36.942
The ark is about to be sealed shut. You're running out of time.

00:12:36.943 --> 00:13:26.638
Checking your heart: who is your Lord? We have a window here. In 2025, a great shaking is coming.

00:13:26.639 --> 00:14:00.078
I've heard some people say it would be a year of war, and that's exactly what I heard: war, war, war. And we will see great financial provision.

00:14:00.079 --> 00:14:30.620
What makes you stand out and show that God is a good God if you're broke, busted, and disgusted, sick, and always depressed? The world is attracted to life.

00:14:30.621 --> 00:14:52.952
That's why they fake it so much in Hollywood with Botox and fillers and face lifts; they're trying to cover up who they truly are.

00:14:52.953 --> 00:15:13.207
But when you have a light on your face and a song in your heart, people see it.

00:15:13.208 --> 00:16:54.017
They feel the presence of the Holy Spirit on you. Material things are never going to fill that empty void in your heart.

00:16:54.018 --> 00:17:17.176
You yield yourself to the Prince of Peace. He's the one who's going to renew your mind from all the hell you've let in.

00:17:17.177 --> 00:17:42.622
Garbage in, garbage out; peace in, peace out. Think on things that are pure and holy.

00:17:42.623 --> 00:17:50.674
People continue to do the same thing expecting different results; that is the definition of insanity.

00:17:50.675 --> 00:18:03.948
You think you're going to fill this hole with money and perversion?

00:18:03.949 --> 00:18:27.755
You're still going to be empty tomorrow. You get wasted at bars and then vomit your guts out.

00:18:27.756 --> 00:18:36.403
The only one that's ever going to satisfy is the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:18:36.404 --> 00:19:27.048
I am addicted to Jesus. I am sold out. He's changed me from the inside out. I have found the source! He is life, joy, and peace.

00:19:27.049 --> 00:20:06.232
As you seek His face, He said, 'Give, and it shall be given unto you.'The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous. Seek first the kingdom.

00:20:06.233 --> 00:21:05.913
He said, 'Brandon, I'll let you have as much overflow as long as it doesn't have you.'I will make you a distribution center if you just yield to me.

00:21:05.914 --> 00:21:31.157
All I need is peace and joy. A vessel leaks, and you've got to keep being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:21:31.158 --> 00:22:00.271
You've got to fill it up with the water of the Word, having fellowship with Him.

00:22:00.272 --> 00:22:33.860
I know there's a lot of you desperate for change in 2025. You have to raise your praise level.

00:22:33.861 --> 00:23:05.228
When praises go up, blessings come down. Keep it vertical with the Lord.

00:23:05.229 --> 00:23:30.835
If you're not in sync with Him on what to do with your money, you'll lose it in a 24-hour period.

00:23:30.836 --> 00:23:53.286
Are you all in for Jesus today? Perfect love casts out all fear. God is our protector.

00:23:53.287 --> 00:24:13.206
We were listening to Pastor Chip tonight about Maria Woodworth-Etter in the 1930s during the Great Depression.

00:24:13.207 --> 00:25:02.804
They had no food, but they set their plates and prayed by faith, and somebody would knock on their door supernaturally.

00:25:02.805 --> 00:25:46.439
We will live in the supernatural in the days ahead. I saw a window of opportunity to get your house in order.

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:55.763
People are going to flee from the East Coast and West Coast to the central part of America for a major revival.

00:25:55.764 --> 00:26:33.569
I saw Woodstock taking place all over the nation. It's a time to get your heart right.

00:26:33.570 --> 00:26:50.664
I want to give everyone an opportunity to accept Jesus. We're going to say the sinner's prayer.

00:26:50.665 --> 00:27:42.939
Romans 10:9-10 says if you confess with your mouth and believe in your heart, you will be saved.

00:27:42.940 --> 00:27:53.991
Say, 'Jesus, I want to make you my Lord and personal savior. I believe You died and rose again.

00:27:53.992 --> 00:28:32.945
Forgive me of my sins. Today I'm turning my back on the world and looking to You.

00:28:32.946 --> 00:29:01.471
Thank You for washing my sins away.'If you said that, you're born again.

00:29:01.472 --> 00:29:44.672
Find a Bible-believing church, get water baptized, and tell people.

00:29:44.673 --> 00:30:42.953
It will help you get strong to stand against the devil. It's time to put on your armor. Feed your faith on the Word.

00:30:42.954 --> 00:30:52.754
Now we're going to pray for President Trump, the inauguration, and the fires in California.

00:30:52.755 --> 00:31:47.036
We take communion. Lord, we thank You that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:31:47.037 --> 00:32:46.334
We plead the blood of Jesus over our finances, jobs, and homes.

00:32:46.335 --> 00:33:00.716
We lift up President Trump and bind the demonic attack concerning this trial.

00:33:00.717 --> 00:33:12.833
We say, 'Satan, get your hands off.'No weapon formed against him shall prosper.

00:33:12.834 --> 00:33:41.052
We pray the angels protect him and his family. We call for a holy conviction over these prosecutors.

00:33:41.053 --> 00:36:03.857
We pray over the fires in California and say, 'Fires, stop now.'We call the angels to put them out.

00:36:03.858 --> 00:37:21.239
We pray for protection against any kind of attacks on this nation. Let everything hidden be revealed.

00:37:21.240 --> 00:38:23.805
We call for revival over this beautiful nation, Asia, the Middle East, and Russia.

00:38:23.806 --> 00:40:16.157
We thank You for the financial outpouring to support the gospel.

00:40:16.158 --> 00:40:28.333
Diana, pray over the babies. Father, we speak to these women's wombs.

00:40:28.334 --> 00:40:51.620
We thank You that everything is functioning as it should. We call for healthy pregnancies and easy deliveries.

00:40:51.621 --> 00:41:35.571
These babies will come forth healed and whole, with no neurological difficulties.

00:41:35.572 --> 00:43:27.434
We pray they have perfect Apgar scores. We pray for godly homes and strong marriages.

00:43:27.435 --> 00:45:40.982
We pray against SAD, Seasonal Affective Disorder. We have the mind of Christ.

00:45:40.983 --> 00:46:54.159
We rebuke autoimmune and thyroid disorders. Today, something good is happening for me!

00:46:54.160 --> 00:47:35.792
We thank You for the blood of Jesus. Lord, we give You praise.

00:47:35.793 --> 00:48:40.934
Amen. If you're new here, please subscribe. It helps the algorithm spread the gospel.

00:48:40.935 --> 00:49:52.947
It's all about getting Jesus spread throughout the whole world.

00:49:52.948 --> 00:50:08.124
Our new Spanish channel, Last Days Español, is going. We have channels in Chinese, Korean, Vietnamese, and Russian.

00:50:08.125 --> 00:51:43.938
We're spreading the word because we're running out of time.

00:51:43.939 --> 00:52:41.637
Thank you for supporting us. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you. God bless you.

